1
00:00:05,674 --> 00:00:08,370
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,444 --> 00:00:12,312
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,381 --> 00:00:16,374
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,719 --> 00:00:19,210
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,288 --> 00:00:23,349
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,425 --> 00:00:27,384
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,864 --> 00:00:33,597
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,303 --> 00:00:37,272
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,708 --> 00:00:41,801
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,544 --> 00:00:43,841
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,179 --> 00:00:46,739
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,790 --> 00:01:00,160
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,362 --> 00:01:01,522
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,597 --> 00:01:05,397
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,734 --> 00:01:10,933
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,206 --> 00:01:12,537
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,608 --> 00:01:14,007
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,076 --> 00:01:20,345
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:31,598 --> 00:01:34,590
<i>The waves of pain are coming faster...</i>

20
00:01:35,102 --> 00:01:38,765
Sasuke, you should quit
the preliminaries!

21
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:40,731
Huh?!

22
00:01:41,742 --> 00:01:43,505
L-Look, you haven't been yourself

23
00:01:43,577 --> 00:01:46,205
ever since you got worked over
by that Orochimaru guy!

24
00:01:46,413 --> 00:01:48,745
Yoroi Akado vs. Sasuke Uchiha

25
00:01:49,783 --> 00:01:51,307
<i>To think it'd be so soon...?!</i>

26
00:01:55,022 --> 00:01:56,683
<i>I couldn't ask for more.</i>

27
00:01:57,758 --> 00:01:59,885
For the 1st battle,

28
00:02:00,427 --> 00:02:03,624
Yoroi Akado and Sasuke Uchiha
have been selected.

29
00:02:04,531 --> 00:02:05,828
No objections, right?

30
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:07,964
- Right!
- No!

31
00:02:09,770 --> 00:02:11,203
<i>The pain won't go away!</i>

32
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,333
<i>It appears the Curse Mark hurts.</i>

33
00:02:17,077 --> 00:02:18,442
Don't use the Sharingan.

34
00:02:20,881 --> 00:02:22,007
So you knew?

35
00:02:23,283 --> 00:02:25,274
If that Curse Mark on
your neck gets out of control,

36
00:02:26,053 --> 00:02:27,611
it could endanger your life.

37
00:02:29,690 --> 00:02:30,622
I believe it.

38
00:02:31,858 --> 00:02:34,884
Well, the match will be
called off at that time.

39
00:02:35,629 --> 00:02:38,097
I'll be coming in to stop it,
so good luck.

40
00:02:39,399 --> 00:02:40,525
<i>Called off, you say?!</i>

41
00:02:43,704 --> 00:02:47,697
<i>It seems this Curse Mark thing</i>
<i>is responding to my Chakra.</i>

42
00:02:48,842 --> 00:02:50,173
<i>In other words, in this match,</i>

43
00:02:50,243 --> 00:02:52,609
<i>I can hardly use even</i>
<i>my regular Jutsu,</i>

44
00:02:52,679 --> 00:02:55,341
<i>not to mention the Sharingan!</i>

45
00:02:58,885 --> 00:03:06,451
<i>However... Yoroi's ability is</i>
<i>the worst for you, Sasuke.</i>

46
00:03:07,227 --> 00:03:09,491
Now then, please begin.

47
00:03:25,645 --> 00:03:28,273
You... my Chakra...

48
00:03:30,584 --> 00:03:32,415
You just noticed now...?

49
00:03:38,091 --> 00:03:44,052
Bushy-Brow's Jealousy -
Lions Barrage Unleashed!

50
00:04:08,055 --> 00:04:10,546
You... my Chakra...

51
00:04:13,193 --> 00:04:14,751
You just noticed now...?

52
00:04:21,968 --> 00:04:26,598
<i>Yes...Yoroi has unorthodox ability</i>
<i>to absorb Chakra.</i>

53
00:04:27,207 --> 00:04:30,199
<i>It's a magnificent art that</i>
<i>absorbs spiritual and physical energy</i>

54
00:04:30,277 --> 00:04:34,509
<i>simply by holding his palm against</i>
<i>an opponent's body.</i>

55
00:04:35,649 --> 00:04:40,677
<i>And, if all of your Chakra</i>
<i>is absorbed, Sasuke,</i>

56
00:04:41,288 --> 00:04:45,554
<i>you'll be forced to rely upon</i>
<i>the power of my Curse Mark...</i>

57
00:04:51,431 --> 00:04:56,494
<i>Now, release that luscious power...!</i>

58
00:04:57,604 --> 00:05:01,040
<i>That is the only way</i>
<i>you have to survive.</i>

59
00:05:03,977 --> 00:05:05,638
You... little!

60
00:05:13,153 --> 00:05:15,417
To think you still have strength left...

61
00:05:15,956 --> 00:05:17,890
Though you're just a guinea pig.

62
00:05:19,493 --> 00:05:20,551
<i>That was a close one...</i>

63
00:05:21,428 --> 00:05:24,829
Put your mind at ease...
I'll end this right away!

64
00:05:43,617 --> 00:05:44,982
What's the matter, what's the matter?!

65
00:05:45,385 --> 00:05:46,511
You already finished?!

66
00:05:52,559 --> 00:05:54,925
<i>His aim is one, close quarter fight.</i>

67
00:05:55,195 --> 00:05:55,854
<i>What should I do!?</i>

68
00:05:56,463 --> 00:05:58,021
<i>At this rate, things will go downhill...</i>

69
00:06:01,868 --> 00:06:05,634
<i>Sasuke Uchiha...</i>
<i>Is this the best you can do?</i>

70
00:06:07,541 --> 00:06:08,439
<i>Sasuke...</i>

71
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,638
Sasuke!

72
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:19,542
You call yourself an Uchiha with that?

73
00:06:21,354 --> 00:06:23,788
Don't be looking so lame!

74
00:06:24,124 --> 00:06:26,058
Give your best!

75
00:06:30,297 --> 00:06:31,195
<i>That guy...</i>

76
00:06:33,633 --> 00:06:34,361
<i>That's it!</i>

77
00:06:35,502 --> 00:06:36,093
Oh!

78
00:06:38,538 --> 00:06:40,768
You can't afford to be inattentive!

79
00:06:42,809 --> 00:06:44,242
I'll finish you with this!

80
00:06:56,790 --> 00:06:58,348
<i>Is this as far as it goes...?</i>

81
00:07:04,931 --> 00:07:05,522
He... vanished?!

82
00:07:14,374 --> 00:07:15,306
<i>That's my...!</i>

83
00:07:16,076 --> 00:07:16,804
<i>What?!</i>

84
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:18,035
<i>Huh?</i>

85
00:07:23,650 --> 00:07:27,552
But then... from here on is my original.

86
00:07:29,089 --> 00:07:29,680
It's over...

87
00:07:30,957 --> 00:07:32,083
The Dancing Leaf Shadow...?!

88
00:07:35,128 --> 00:07:35,787
Eat this!

89
00:07:45,338 --> 00:07:48,865
<i>Damn it...!</i>
<i>It's responding every time...</i>

90
00:08:10,530 --> 00:08:11,497
<i>Please...!</i>

91
00:08:14,234 --> 00:08:15,201
<i>I'm begging you...</i>

92
00:08:17,504 --> 00:08:18,368
<i>Stop!</i>

93
00:08:23,910 --> 00:08:28,540
<i>You! Sasuke!</i>
<i>Don't be looking so lame!</i>

94
00:08:30,317 --> 00:08:32,478
<i>To think they'd be worried about me...</i>

95
00:08:34,287 --> 00:08:35,345
<i>Is this it...?</i>

96
00:08:37,791 --> 00:08:41,557
<i>I won't be swallowed up...</i>
<i>by this thing...</i>

97
00:08:41,861 --> 00:08:42,793
<i>No way!</i>

98
00:08:54,607 --> 00:08:55,631
<i>The Curse Mark receded!?</i>

99
00:08:58,345 --> 00:08:59,175
Here I go!

100
00:09:04,617 --> 00:09:05,584
<i>You're weak!</i>

101
00:09:08,722 --> 00:09:09,484
You're weak.

102
00:09:21,468 --> 00:09:22,366
I'm not done, yet!

103
00:09:25,472 --> 00:09:26,564
Lions Barrage!

104
00:09:54,901 --> 00:09:56,869
<i>There's no need to check.</i>

105
00:10:18,057 --> 00:10:20,355
I'm stopping the match from
going any further...

106
00:10:21,394 --> 00:10:25,728
Therefore, the winner of the
first battle, Sasuke Uchiha...

107
00:10:26,566 --> 00:10:27,760
passes the preliminaries!

108
00:10:28,835 --> 00:10:29,665
Yes!

109
00:10:44,957 --> 00:10:47,016
Well. Good job...

110
00:10:50,996 --> 00:10:53,157
<i>Before that Lions Barrage,</i>

111
00:10:53,632 --> 00:10:55,122
<i>your movements were that</i>
<i>of Guy's Taijutsu...</i>

112
00:10:56,802 --> 00:10:58,997
<i>So you copied it with the Sharingan</i>

113
00:10:59,237 --> 00:11:01,671
<i>when you wrangled that one time</i>
<i>with that Lee kid?</i>

114
00:11:06,812 --> 00:11:11,112
Sasuke! You, you...

115
00:11:11,249 --> 00:11:13,308
won in a lame way!

116
00:11:13,385 --> 00:11:15,910
Look at you, all battered up!
You idiot!

117
00:11:16,755 --> 00:11:18,916
Man, that loser...

118
00:11:22,427 --> 00:11:24,725
<i>Sasuke...Thank goodness.</i>

119
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:27,628
<i>Okay, I'll win, too!</i>

120
00:11:31,703 --> 00:11:35,605
<i>Lee... Because of you,</i>
<i>I've managed to save my neck.</i>

121
00:11:36,341 --> 00:11:37,569
<i>Things would've gotten hairy</i>

122
00:11:37,642 --> 00:11:39,405
<i>if I hadn't seen your technique</i>
<i>in close quarters combat.</i>

123
00:11:48,687 --> 00:11:52,282
<i>But it doesn't appear to be a technique</i>
<i>that I can use heavily.</i>

124
00:11:53,325 --> 00:11:59,753
<i>I see... So before, he copied a part</i>
<i>of the technique I only used once?</i>

125
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,558
<i>Sharingan!</i>

126
00:12:07,406 --> 00:12:09,237
<i>That's your ability...</i>

127
00:12:10,175 --> 00:12:12,643
<i>Sasuke... you're quite a person.</i>

128
00:12:13,145 --> 00:12:15,272
<i>You get rapidly stronger...</i>

129
00:12:16,882 --> 00:12:19,612
<i>I kind of...feel a bit of fear.</i>

130
00:12:24,156 --> 00:12:27,250
<i>For a sequence of</i>
<i>high speed Taijutsu Lotus movements,</i>

131
00:12:27,492 --> 00:12:30,290
<i>it's impossible to acquire this</i>
<i>without training</i>

132
00:12:30,362 --> 00:12:32,193
<i>that whittles away flesh and blood.</i>

133
00:12:32,631 --> 00:12:34,724
<i>No matter how much you</i>
<i>use the Sharingan,</i>

134
00:12:35,100 --> 00:12:37,933
<i>it can't just be mastered in</i>
<i>a short space of time...</i>

135
00:12:38,370 --> 00:12:41,305
<i>Moreover, his idea for that</i>
<i>finishing move...</i>

136
00:12:43,175 --> 00:12:48,909
<i>Kakashi... this boy reminds me</i>
<i>of when you were a kid...</i>

137
00:12:54,820 --> 00:12:57,311
<i>Last year's number one rookie</i>
<i>was Neji Hyuga.</i>

138
00:12:58,590 --> 00:13:01,184
<i>This year's number one rookie</i>
<i>is Sasuke Uchiha.</i>

139
00:13:02,561 --> 00:13:04,392
<i>I wonder which one is stronger...?</i>

140
00:13:07,632 --> 00:13:09,065
<i>Really, he's something else.</i>

141
00:13:10,102 --> 00:13:13,401
<i>To think he'd develop the true power</i>
<i>of the Sharingan in situation like this...</i>

142
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:18,071
<i>What's most to be feared...</i>
<i>is the Uchiha ability?</i>

143
00:13:23,648 --> 00:13:24,672
<i>That was surprising...</i>

144
00:13:25,417 --> 00:13:27,385
<i>To think he brought the Curse Mark</i>
<i>that was getting out of control</i>

145
00:13:27,452 --> 00:13:29,283
<i>into submission with his will...</i>

146
00:13:37,162 --> 00:13:39,187
<i>Tsk. Again?</i>

147
00:13:41,166 --> 00:13:43,191
It just makes it more interesting!

148
00:13:44,169 --> 00:13:47,764
Yeah! He is Sasuke after all...

149
00:13:48,273 --> 00:13:50,241
<i>This is as far as we'll go...</i>

150
00:13:50,976 --> 00:13:52,637
I'm hungry...

151
00:13:53,645 --> 00:13:54,543
W-Wow!

152
00:13:55,881 --> 00:13:57,405
Nothing special.

153
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:04,018
<i>Magnificent...</i>

154
00:14:08,927 --> 00:14:10,019
Sasuke Uchiha...

155
00:14:10,629 --> 00:14:14,326
We medics will give you
the best of treatment.

156
00:14:14,900 --> 00:14:17,164
You guys are out of your territory.

157
00:14:17,469 --> 00:14:18,026
Huh?!

158
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:20,333
I'll take him under my care...

159
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:24,140
Now, I'll take you into the back...

160
00:14:25,810 --> 00:14:27,141
and seal the Curse Mark.

161
00:14:27,345 --> 00:14:29,279
Can we wait until
the preliminaries are over?!

162
00:14:29,748 --> 00:14:32,012
I want to watch the matches
of those who will remain in the main battle.

163
00:14:32,450 --> 00:14:33,348
No!

164
00:14:34,252 --> 00:14:35,719
Don't get so heated.

165
00:14:36,154 --> 00:14:37,280
If we let things be
any further,

166
00:14:37,355 --> 00:14:39,846
the situation might become irrevocable.

167
00:14:40,125 --> 00:14:42,685
I won't accommodate you anymore.

168
00:14:44,229 --> 00:14:45,253
Now then, come on...

169
00:14:51,069 --> 00:14:52,001
<i>Sasuke...</i>

170
00:15:00,212 --> 00:15:00,837
<i>Hm?</i>

171
00:15:25,036 --> 00:15:28,164
Sakura... Speaking of which,
during the match...

172
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:31,739
did you see something that looked
like a strange wound on Sasuke's neck?

173
00:15:31,977 --> 00:15:32,443
What?

174
00:15:36,081 --> 00:15:37,412
<i>Please promise me...</i>

175
00:15:38,149 --> 00:15:40,208
<i>Don't say anything about</i>
<i>this bruise to Naruto.</i>

176
00:15:40,418 --> 00:15:41,043
<i>What?</i>

177
00:15:42,787 --> 00:15:45,221
<i>Listen... this is also teamwork.</i>

178
00:15:45,657 --> 00:15:48,854
<i>It won't do to have him</i>
<i>unnecessarily worried.</i>

179
00:15:50,128 --> 00:15:52,426
I-I don't know either.

180
00:15:53,365 --> 00:15:54,354
I see...

181
00:15:57,535 --> 00:15:59,332
Umm, now then...

182
00:15:59,971 --> 00:16:02,030
We will get right to it and
begin the second match.

183
00:16:23,228 --> 00:16:24,855
Abumi Zaku vs. Shino Aburame

184
00:16:27,299 --> 00:16:28,698
Which weakling is it?!

185
00:16:39,044 --> 00:16:40,102
Both of you, come forward.

186
00:16:44,482 --> 00:16:47,883
We will now begin the second match.

187
00:16:51,356 --> 00:16:53,153
<i>That's the Sound Ninja...</i>

188
00:16:54,092 --> 00:16:56,356
<i>The guy who had both</i>
<i>his arms broken by Sasuke!</i>

189
00:17:02,367 --> 00:17:04,198
<i>It seems like you're proud</i>
<i>of your arms...</i>

190
00:17:04,869 --> 00:17:05,597
<i>You!</i>

191
00:17:07,339 --> 00:17:08,363
<i>S-Stop it!</i>

192
00:17:19,551 --> 00:17:21,178
<i>He's going to fight with those arms?</i>

193
00:17:24,289 --> 00:17:26,052
I wonder if Shino is going to be okay...

194
00:17:26,558 --> 00:17:29,220
He's fine. He's strong

195
00:17:29,461 --> 00:17:30,052
What...?

196
00:17:31,129 --> 00:17:33,757
I'd square off with anybody except him...

197
00:17:36,634 --> 00:17:38,761
Now then, please begin.

198
00:17:39,371 --> 00:17:41,271
<i>Now, Zaku...</i>

199
00:17:41,639 --> 00:17:43,800
<i>How you fight will be a sight to see...</i>

200
00:18:02,527 --> 00:18:05,894
If you fight here,
you'll be finished...

201
00:18:06,965 --> 00:18:07,624
Withdraw!

202
00:18:12,203 --> 00:18:14,933
Somehow, this one still works, so...

203
00:18:19,811 --> 00:18:22,439
One arm is enough to take care of you!

204
00:18:26,818 --> 00:18:29,480
You can't beat me with
just one arm.

205
00:18:29,788 --> 00:18:31,255
Stop pestering me!

206
00:18:34,325 --> 00:18:35,292
Take this!

207
00:18:35,827 --> 00:18:37,522
Slicing Sound Wave!

208
00:19:11,329 --> 00:19:12,159
Okay.

209
00:19:14,199 --> 00:19:16,599
Hang in there.
It'll be over right away.

210
00:19:28,947 --> 00:19:30,312
Curse Sealing!

211
00:19:57,408 --> 00:20:00,434
Next time, even if that Curse Mark
starts kicking in again...

212
00:20:01,546 --> 00:20:04,538
the power of this Curse Sealing
should suppress it.

213
00:20:06,751 --> 00:20:12,781
However, this Sealing Jutsu makes
the strength of your will its foundation.

214
00:20:13,558 --> 00:20:16,083
If something happens like
you not believing in your own strength

215
00:20:16,194 --> 00:20:18,492
and that will were to weaken...

216
00:20:19,330 --> 00:20:21,389
the Curse Mark will
once again start to rage.

217
00:20:27,539 --> 00:20:28,767
Out of character.

218
00:20:28,840 --> 00:20:30,569
It appears he's quite tired...

219
00:20:31,209 --> 00:20:34,178
To think you've become able to
handle Sealing Jutsu...

220
00:20:36,648 --> 00:20:39,617
You've grown, eh, Kakashi...?

221
00:20:44,656 --> 00:20:45,520
You...

222
00:20:53,531 --> 00:20:56,728
Long time no see, Kakashi.

223
00:20:58,870 --> 00:20:59,859
Orochimaru...

224
00:21:05,743 --> 00:21:10,476
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

225
00:21:10,581 --> 00:21:18,681
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

226
00:21:19,757 --> 00:21:28,290
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

227
00:21:28,899 --> 00:21:36,601
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

228
00:21:38,008 --> 00:21:43,537
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

229
00:21:43,614 --> 00:21:47,380
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

230
00:21:47,451 --> 00:21:51,012
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

231
00:21:51,488 --> 00:21:59,896
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

232
00:22:00,297 --> 00:22:05,360
<i>when you want to cry,</i>
<i>and you want to run away</i>

233
00:22:05,436 --> 00:22:09,839
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

234
00:22:10,007 --> 00:22:13,670
<i>Just sing.</i>

235
00:22:13,977 --> 00:22:19,074
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

236
00:22:19,216 --> 00:22:21,343
<i>The two are one</i>

237
00:22:21,452 --> 00:22:27,721
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

238
00:22:28,325 --> 00:22:33,319
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

239
00:22:37,722 --> 00:22:38,780
This is surprising.

240
00:22:39,424 --> 00:22:41,119
I never thought you'd appear.

241
00:22:41,659 --> 00:22:45,117
Why are you after Sasuke?
What's your purpose?!

242
00:22:46,130 --> 00:22:48,496
Even though you're one of
the legendary three Ninja,

243
00:22:48,700 --> 00:22:49,962
I must not retreat.

244
00:22:50,635 --> 00:22:54,230
I'll stop you here,
even if it costs my life!

245
00:22:55,940 --> 00:22:59,603
Next episode: "Kakashi and Orochimaru:
Face-to-Face!"

246
00:22:59,711 --> 00:23:01,975
Well, it's sink or swim.
